      <title>荷兰合作银行的 Foley 表示，法国僵局不应给市场带来安慰</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-gridlock-shouldn-t-comfort-markets-rabobank-s-foley-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰合作银行货币策略师简·福利 (Jane Foley) 表示，周日法国大选后出现悬浮议会的前景不应该让投资者感到高兴，因为这将意味着预算陷入僵局。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/french-gridlock-shouldn-t-comfort-markets-rabobank-s-foley-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:49:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚企业监管机构面临参议院拆分要求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/australia-corporate-watchdog-faces-senate-calls-for-breakup</link>
      <description><![CDATA[作为旨在增强执法能力的改革的一部分，澳大利亚的企业监管机构应该一分为二，举报人应该获得赔偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/australia-corporate-watchdog-faces-senate-calls-for-breakup</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:28:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>勒庞寻求多数席位，而竞争对手则联手阻止她</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在周日举行的法国立法选举最后一轮中，玛丽娜·勒庞领导的国民联盟正在努力争取绝对多数，而竞争对手则在竭尽全力阻止极右翼政党掌权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/le-pen-seeks-majority-as-rival-groups-band-together-to-stop-her</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:27:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>法国大选动荡之际，对冲基金抛售欧洲股票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/hedge-funds-sold-european-stocks-amid-france-election-turmoil</link>
      <description><![CDATA[高盛集团的顶级经纪部门称，对冲基金 6 月份抛售欧洲股票，扭转了上个月的购买趋势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/hedge-funds-sold-european-stocks-amid-france-election-turmoil</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:11:46 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日元贬值、通货膨胀导致日本税收收入创下新高</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/japan-tax-revenue-sets-another-record-amid-weak-yen-inflation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[截止 3 月份的财年，日本的税收收入再创历史新高，这一积极结果部分得益于日元疲软和通胀持续上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/japan-tax-revenue-sets-another-record-amid-weak-yen-inflation</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 07:08:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>世界银行下调泰国经济增长预期，支持央行维持利率稳定</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/world-bank-cuts-thai-growth-outlook-backs-central-bank-in-keeping-rate-steady</link>
      <description><![CDATA[世界银行表示，泰国应该等待经济形势更加明朗后再放松货币政策，这实际上支持泰国央行的利率政策，尽管泰国政府呼吁尽早放松货币政策。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-03/world-bank-cuts-thai-growth-outlook-backs-central-bank-in-keeping-rate-steady</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 03 Jul 2024 05:56:40 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华尔街创纪录后欧洲股市上涨：市场综述</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美联储主席杰罗姆·鲍威尔表示通胀正在重回下行通道后，市场对美国降息持乐观态度，欧洲股市上涨，追随标准普尔 500 指数收盘纪录。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 22:19:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>交易员纷纷押注特朗普推动的美国债券收益率上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/traders-flock-to-a-trump-fueled-bet-on-higher-us-treasury-yields</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着华尔街开始为唐纳德·特朗普可能重返白宫做出调整，规模 27 万亿美元的美国国债市场交易员们押注长期债券收益率将会上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/traders-flock-to-a-trump-fueled-bet-on-higher-us-treasury-yields</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 20:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>英美资源集团考虑在火灾后出售煤炭资产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/anglo-considers-options-to-sell-coal-assets-after-australia-fire</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在其澳大利亚旗舰煤矿发生爆炸后，英美资源集团正在考虑推进其煤炭业务出售的多种方案，包括出售个别资产或将受损业务排除在潜在交易之外。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/anglo-considers-options-to-sell-coal-assets-after-australia-fire</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:42:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>电动汽车市场放缓，巴斯夫取消智利投资计划</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/basf-pulls-plug-on-potential-chile-investments-amid-lithium-rout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于全球电动汽车普及速度放缓导致电池金属价格下跌，德国化学品制造商巴斯夫公司放弃了投资智利锂矿资产的计划。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-07-02/basf-pulls-plug-on-potential-chile-investments-amid-lithium-rout</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 02 Jul 2024 17:31:47 GMT</pubDate>
